        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>A spray of rainbow light beams cascades from your open hand. Each creature in the area must roll 1d8 on the table below to see which beam affects it, then attempt a saving throw of the indicated type. The table notes any additional traits that apply to each type of ray. If a creature is struck by multiple beams, it uses the same d20 result for all its saving throws. For all rays, a successful saving throw negates the effect for that creature.</p>\n<h3><strong>Prismatic Spray</strong></h3>\n<table style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 365px; color: #191813; height: 155px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: white; height: 25px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #522e2c;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">1d8</strong></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: white; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #522e2c; height: 25px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Color</strong></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: white; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #522e2c; height: 25px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Save</strong></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: white; height: 25px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #522e2c;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Effects (Traits)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Red</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Reflex</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">50 fire damage (fire)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 17px;\">Orange</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 17px;\">Reflex</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">60 acid damge (acid)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Yellow</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Reflex</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">70 electricity damage (electricity)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 19px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 19px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 19px;\">Green</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 19px;\">Fortitude</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 19px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">30 poison damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 minute (poison)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Blue</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Fortitude</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">Affected as if by @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Flesh to Stone]{Flesh to Stone}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 17px;\">Indigo</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 17px;\">Will</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">Confused, as the @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Warp Mind]{Warp Mind} spell (mental)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Violet</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1; height: 17px;\">Will</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #f6f1e1;\">Slowed for 1 minute; if a critical failure, sent to another plane, as @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Plane Shift]{Plane Shift}<em> </em>(teleportation)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 26px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 66px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 17px;\">Potent beam</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 64px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8; height: 17px;\">-<br /><</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; height: 17px; width: 208px; text-align: center; background-color: #eee5c8;\">Affected by two beams - roll twice, rerolling any duplicates or results of 8</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
